  "name": "RPlog_The_Mikassa_Incident",
  "title": "The Mikassa Incident",
  "summary": "Admiral Danik Kreldin leads an Imperial task force, spearheaded by the Star Destroyers Conqueror and Nemesis, into the Mikassa system to seize the Caspian Democratic Union's naval station. His old nemesis Captain Axel Vichten, now commissioned in the CDU Navy aboard the modified Carrack Purgatory, refuses to surrender and vows reprisals against Imperial supply lines. A sprawling space battle erupts amid a minefield: Imperial Scimitar bombers and TIE fighters savage the evacuating CDU transports while CDU Z-100s and A-wings cut through the attackers, claiming Imperial pilots like the doomed ensign Deyal Huxlo. The hidden CDU light cruiser Breslau ambushes the interdictor Oppressor, and the wounded frigate Thresher makes a kamikaze run that cripples the Nemesis, buying time for the transports to escape to hyperspace. Outnumbered, Axel orders the Purgatory to retreat, and the CDU fleet jumps away in near-unison, leaving the Empire to board and occupy the battered Mikassa station.",
